title: Add a Command to Tiddler Toolbar
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

* Every tiddler tagged with `$:/tags/ViewToolbar` will appear in the Tiddlywiki sidebar
* The position in the sidebar can be determined using the `list-after` and `list-before` field
* Normally this tiddler includes a button to take action on click! See the `comments` plugin in ~Tiddlywiki 5.1.18-pre
